sources.title: Way into «Saturn» | WAR DRAMA
sources.description:
Based on the work by V. Ardamatsky "Saturn" is almost invisible". The first episode of the two-part action film tells about the penetration of our intelligence officer into the highly classified organization "Saturn", who won the trust of the leaders of the Hitlerite sabotage center and transmitted an important message to Moscow.

Year of production: 1967

Director: Azarov Villen
Scriptwriters: Bleiman Mikhail, Ardamatsky Vasily, Azarov Villen
Composer: Flyarkovsky Alexander
DOP: Dyatlov Mark
Production designer: Ushakov Semyon

Cast: Georgy Zhenov, Vladimir Pokrovsky, Valentina Talyzina, Vladimir Kashpur, Nikolai Grabbe, Vladimir Muravyov, Arkady Tolbuzin, Nikolai Prokopovich, Grigory Gai, Boris Yurchenko, Gennady Yukhtin, Vladimir Ferapontov, Evgeny Kuznetsov, Mikhail Volkov, Lyudmila Shaposhnikova
